    <item>
      <title>一封來自高中好友的來信</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/posts/friend-plus7_en/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/posts/friend-plus7_en/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;slug: friend-plus7_en&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;letter-from-7&#34;&gt;Letter from +7&lt;a href=&#34;#letter-from-7&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;2026.05.07&#xA;she said&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;What I want to say is&#xA;Every time I see you convert your ideals into action, it drives me forward.&#xA;It&amp;rsquo;s amazing. We obviously don&amp;rsquo;t contact each other very often.&#xA;So you have always been a friend that I am very proud of.&#xA;You will attract equally good people as you said in your writing.&#xA;Like me :D)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
